From df40ce8519a9f34748c7200dcf29170776582f2d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andrew Yong <me@ndoo.sg>
Date: Sat, 2 Aug 2025 18:50:01 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] arm64: dts: rockchip: Add support for Radxa CM5 on CM4 IO
 carrier

- Move common includes to rk3588s-radxa-cm5.dtsi
- Move peripherals which are on-board the Radxa CM5 rather than the Radxa CM5 I/O board from rk3588s-radxa-cm5-io.dts to rk3588s-radxa-cm5.dtsi
  - Regulators: All RK806 PMIC rails
  - GMAC: gmac1 (RTL8211FS)
- Add peripherals which are on-board the Radxa CM5 to rk3588s-radxa-cm5.dtsi
  - Voltage rails:
    - vcc_sysin
    - vcc_1v1_nldo_s3
  - EEPROM:
    - BL24C16F
- Sync RK806 PMIC regulators with downstream dtsi and other Radxa RK3588S boards
- Add DTS for rk3588s-radxa-cm5-rpi-cm4-io

Signed-off-by: Andrew Yong <me@ndoo.sg>
